Paper: hep-th/9603132

Date: 1996-03-19

Title: Generalized Fractional Statistics

Authors: G. Kaniadakis, A. Lavagno and P. Quarati

Comments: 4 pages, RevTex

We link, by means of a semiclassical approach, the fractional statistics ofparticles obeying the Haldane exclusion principle to the Tsallis statistics andderive a generalized quantum entropy and its associated statistics.